  </recommends>
  
  <description>
    <p>Resticity is a frontend application for managing restic backups. It covers many of restic's features via a modern GUI such as: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Scheduling backup and prune jobs</li>
      <li>Browsing snapshots</li>
      <li>Restoring files</li>
      <li>Configuring repositories</li>
      <li>Notifications and Hooks</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
